; npm settings for this project
;
; Why this file exists:
;   The portfolio is on React 17 (CRA 5). Newer first-party packages — most
;   notably @vercel/analytics — list React 18+ as a peer dependency. They
;   work fine with React 17 in practice, but npm 7+ refuses to install them
;   without an explicit override.
;
; Locally we'd type `npm install --legacy-peer-deps`. On Vercel's build
; pipeline we don't get to pass flags to `npm install`, so we set it here.
; This is the smallest, most explicit fix; no engines fudging, no fork.
legacy-peer-deps=true
